Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#26 回归忧国之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空袭又开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.34,0:00:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人拦截到船员的通讯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.18,0:00:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有可以窃听的电波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.28,0:00:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.45,0:00:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立刻收集电脑空间内的可使用区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.02,0:00:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保能够传送300万人记忆和Ghost的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.82,0:00:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？这么突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.99,0:00:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了，动作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.83,0:00:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情，能办到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.27,0:01:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.57,0:01:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我找不到其它可以拯救难民的方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.70,0:01:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了...了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.68,0:01:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚叫支援AI在电脑空间确保可使用的区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.21,0:01:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完毕之后，就开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.48,0:01:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借由将Ghost整个传送到网络上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.42,0:01:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设我们可以活下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没有电子脑化的人怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.26,0:01:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对亲友当中有这类人的人来说\N应该很难接受这个结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们大概会对我感到失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.57,0:01:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行离开出岛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.71,0:01:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种状况之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.47,0:01:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指导者的任务常常既重大又充满不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.91,0:01:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在不得不指引多数人的立场上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.52,0:01:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会因情况被迫做出独断的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.69,0:01:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些，他们应该也会了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.32,0:02:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是这样，就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.86,0:02:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我到少校那边的最短路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.20,0:02:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是往大桥去了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.27,0:02:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.51,0:02:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.65,0:02:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核导弹会不会趁空袭后的混乱发射呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从潜艇几乎没有通讯的状况来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.66,0:02:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射时间或许早就决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.19,0:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从宙斯盾舰的距离以及微机械散布的时机来观察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.66,0:02:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AM 10:00 这个时间很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，你们实际上是怎么想的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把难民的记忆上传到网络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能够维持Ghost存在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.02,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆虽然是生命活动很重要的要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，没有Ghost就只是单纯的数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.26,0:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，少校不是把一线\N希望寄托在这上面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.36,0:03:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也知道，可是这实在\N是很乱来的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.13,0:03:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是继续做下去，也没办法\N救巴特先生他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.40,0:03:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，我觉得应该不\N要理会少校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 咦？你在说什么啊！\N- 不懂你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那该怎么办？\N- 我做不到啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不回应我的呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热线明明是通的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就表示……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.79,0:03:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是国会解散重新改选时打选战的广告牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我从未被如此刻薄的对待过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高仓既然做到这个地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要用我的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾这个局势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.31,0:04:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要跟哪里联系呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第8个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.46,0:04:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种运算，我可是高手中的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.53,0:04:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再搞定一个，就肯定能在\N导弹轨道上布下弹幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然照你说的，违反少校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，进行卫星坠落作业\N真的是正确的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.14,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明进行得很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.61,0:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.61,0:04:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说不定是搭载我们AI的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是美帝的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.26,0:04:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看来好像是借用了\N从日本发射的美帝卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果安保条约缔不缔结\N还不是得听那些家伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.50,0:05:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校为什么要把我们的AI放在那种地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.71,0:05:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是想反过来\N对美帝搞谍报之类的工作吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.71,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然搞不清楚那么多\N但这下可伤脑筋了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须跟大家一起去某个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.97,0:05:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.84,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校他们的事情就拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就真的是一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.87,0:06:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.91,0:06:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会折纸鹤吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.71,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸鹤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.88,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只用一只左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用控制软体\N任何人都会折的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会折吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.89,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:37.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,228)}{\fad(300,400)}I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,240)}{\fad(300,400)}作词：Ilaria
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,252)}{\fad(300,400)}作曲：菅野洋子(Yoko kanno)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,264)}{\fad(300,400)}演唱：Ilaria graziano
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是依靠孤独生活下去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直没问，叫什么名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假名倒是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你也是一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:56.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nell' illusione ho creduto alla mia forza inesorabile\N在梦幻中，我相信自己无畏的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难民帮我取了好几个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.14,0:07:01.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,e inevitabilmente sono diventata debole\N却软弱到无法逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然是为了拯救他们\N才和他们一起行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也许只是为了填补孤独
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.74,0:07:07.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ora sento gli eventi si transformano e so già\N我现在所能感知的，是那变换的时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才跟他们在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到最后还是没能填补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.84,0:07:17.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,di emozioni che aprono ricordi lontani\N强烈的感情唤起久远的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为即使被人依赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己却无法依赖别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有可以交心的对象吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.54,0:07:23.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nell'anima ritrovo la speranza che nel corpo stanco ormai\N灵魂重新感受希望，而精疲力竭的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能说是没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.22,0:07:30.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha smesso di vibrare come un fuoco spento dal mio pianto\N却如同泪水浇熄的火焰般停止跳跃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直……都在寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.24,0:07:36.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tra le mani un filo d'acqua porterò con me e\N用双手汲取，哪怕是一掬水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.83,0:07:43.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nel deserto un filo d'erba sopravviverà\N沙漠里就会有些许的草生存下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹不会飞到大桥附近来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌，快点过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,gridare contro gli occhi spenti e gelidi\N我对着他寒冷似冰的眼睛哭喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.89,0:07:59.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,per essere sempre di più\N总有一天会比现在更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.98,0:08:07.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,oltrepassare mondi inespugnabili\N超越磐石般的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.45,0:08:13.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,senza temere nulla più...\N为了不再畏惧虚无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.73,0:08:17.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,emeregere dal fondo per lottare e poi\N挣扎着想从沉沦中飞升起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.11,0:08:28.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,salire in alto più che mai\N升至前所未有的高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.21,0:08:36.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,guardare nel futuro e sorridere\N望着未来而微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.74,0:08:41.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,con una nuova identità\N与全新的自我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.29,0:08:52.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fino a quando il sole sorgerà...\N待到太阳升起之时……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素子！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.47,0:09:03.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.55,0:09:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.41,0:09:25.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,228)}{\fad(300,400)}"手のひらを太陽に(手心向太阳)"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.71,0:09:24.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,240)}{\fad(300,400)}作词:やなせたかし
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.81,0:09:24.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,252)}{\fad(300,400)}作曲:いずみたく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.11,0:09:24.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,264)}{\fad(300,400)}原唱:岛谷瞳(Hitomi Shimatani)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.94,0:09:28.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.81,0:09:33.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きているから 悲しいんだ\N因为活着才会悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.18,0:09:40.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手のひらを太陽に 透かしてみれば\N让阳光透过你的手掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.78,0:09:48.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まっかに流れる 僕の血潮\N我的热血鲜红地流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.16,0:09:52.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みみずだって おけらだって\N不管是蚯蚓还是蝼蛄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这种事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あめんぼだって\N或者是水蝇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.40,0:10:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家一定\N是有Ghost的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.40,0:10:00.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなみんな 生きているんだ\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，普路托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友達なんだ\N都是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.51,0:10:08.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.45,0:10:12.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きているから わらうんだ\N因为活着才会欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.48,0:10:16.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上传：全体塔奇克马的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.39,0:10:20.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きているから うれしいんだ\N因为活着才会快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.69,0:10:28.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手のひらを太陽に 透かしてみれば\N让阳光透过你的手掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.33,0:10:35.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まっかに流れる 僕の血潮\N我的热血鲜红地流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.67,0:10:40.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,とんぼだって かえるだって\N不管是蜻蜓还是青蛙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.28,0:10:44.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みつばちだって\N或者是蜜蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.58,0:10:49.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなみんな 生きているんだ 友だち...\N我们大家都活着，都是好朋友……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事，普路托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.86,0:11:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子，塔奇克马跟卫星\N一起去撞核弹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止了最糟糕的事态发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的情况，我不太了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.17,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎因为部下的牺牲\N阻止了核导弹的发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个，刚刚您提到的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹毁了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.06,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正茅葺的行动将\N促使冷战构造完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.37,0:11:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，这样一来他就当不上英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.84,0:11:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个爆炸是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了塔奇克马的歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小鬼帮我们挡下来了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.67,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AI采取了跟我的命令不同的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校，你没事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马它们……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果总理联系的地方……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.03,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，现在必须先抓住\N官房长官与合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.27,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事也有可能在我们\N有生之年都不能公开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.77,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先迅速进行，事后处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.91,0:12:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官房长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.82,0:13:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您应该知道我们到这里来的理由吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是政变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.26,0:13:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是以战争为借口的屠杀行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法眼睁睁看着他们用核弹自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.07,0:13:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写下这个剧本的应该是您\N还有内厅的合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合田？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.11,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在考虑国家未来的前提下\N提前缔结新安保条约而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场跟难民之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.55,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.82,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来，您将在非公开状态下\N接受严格查问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就有心理准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.29,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我预料的更像个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.66,0:13:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道你感情用事\N跑去向哪边求助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个国家不依靠美帝\N是无法存活下去的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您恐怕有什么误会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎核弹没有爆炸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要发射第二枚吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.41,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.38,0:14:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认从东北方南下的飞机\N属于哪一方再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.09,0:14:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是机身上如果\N有八一徽标的话……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.06,0:14:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身独立，而至一国独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.06,0:14:21.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出自福泽谕吉《劝学》，日本当代政治名言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自始至终，就是这样思考和行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.84,0:14:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茅葺政权将一如既往\N在同美帝、美俄联盟、中国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.34,0:14:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及亚洲、E.U(欧盟)各国\N保持同等政治距离之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照独自的判断行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸索在联合国的协调路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.10,0:14:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航空自卫军的秘密部队么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认到日本方面的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带他走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总理命令我们来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.09,0:15:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把刀，请物归原主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤、帕兹、博玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校，你没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.21,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，要麻烦你们\N向自卫军汇报详细情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是公安9课的石川？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你把那个交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.59,0:16:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们9课可是最擅长打架和情报战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴隶之国要是怠于侍奉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消费之国必然会致饥饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.14,0:16:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不足虽然让劳动制造业获利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.44,0:16:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是过度主张权力\N资本主义的血脉将会硬化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.21,0:16:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国虽然彻头彻尾自称是资本主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.08,0:16:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际却是理想化的社会主义国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.69,0:17:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是累积了废物\N就需要能够操作血液分离的大脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.76,0:17:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点对歌颂自由平等的贵国来说\N应该也是一样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是真心话和场面话还得区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.41,0:17:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必这么急着去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒卷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合田一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你涉嫌犯有预备或阴谋内乱罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.13,0:17:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及预备或阴谋触犯\N私自对外国发动战争罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你跟我们走一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.00,0:17:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官房长官大致已经承认所涉罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你最后的导演也宣告失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.48,0:17:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，现在逮捕我已经没有意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.62,0:18:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与官房长官之间无论\N何时都是Stand Alone的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.25,0:18:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况我亲手写的报告书\N现在应该已经送到警察厅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.99,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这种犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.60,0:18:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑法上规定只要自首 \N其罪行就一概不问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.34,0:18:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去需要我才能的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.14,0:18:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要这样做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有总理的手谕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总理对你的能力给予了很高评价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，当这种能力有可能\N流失到国外的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.72,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总理要求我们全力阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.19,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情况甚至不惜射杀目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意，只是口头威胁罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.70,0:18:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是……！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.69,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙！从什么时候\N开始介入这件事的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.83,0:19:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快，不能让他被灭口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.74,0:19:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸鹤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来，这个微机械还真有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以死得毫无痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你是个让人感兴趣的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，对我们而言你是危险因素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.44,0:20:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵国不需要\N有领导魅力却无法控制的领袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.61,0:20:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有顺从的消费者就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……先走……了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里偷懒呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.41,0:20:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到新浜4区跟阿兹玛与普路托会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.68,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要求的追加预算都通过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻壳车，确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ウチコマ：漫画Ghost in the Shell中的攻壳车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes，Sir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事件，造成了很多牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.13,0:21:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难民问题退回到了原点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.10,0:21:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茅葺总理主张的独立、共同竞争路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于国民来说也是荆棘之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.54,0:21:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后\N会越来越需要我们这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.08,0:21:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一副事不关己的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.95,0:21:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校，你该不会已经看破红尘了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.79,0:21:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.82,0:21:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到第329期国家审议会\N已经通过预算的报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止樱花的24小时监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始返回工作岗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.60,0:21:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.83,0:21:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经快无聊死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.04,0:21:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是事先开着暖气就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校就是要这样才对嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简报怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用脑潜入来做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你先去负责指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等一下过去会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.39,0:22:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.13,0:22:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不……没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轻言细语中穿梭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当黑影升起时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心海的表面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.62,0:22:02.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回音回荡不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.36,0:22:40.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人可责怪的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.00,0:22:51.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林里的空洞寂静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.65,0:23:11.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树根在地底深处交缠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.03,0:23:20.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轻言细语中穿梭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.57,0:23:25.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当黑影升起时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.44,0:23:31.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到某人叹息的表面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.18,0:23:36.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐喊的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.92,0:23:45.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂静正在哭泣…\N正在哭泣…
